#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an11.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an11.10:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 11 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 11 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an11.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Nissayavagga "
msgstr "1. Dependence "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an11.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Moranivāpasutta "
msgstr "10. At the Peacocks’ Feeding Ground "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an11.10:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati moranivāpe paribbājakārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, at the monastery of the wanderers in the peacocks’ feeding ground. "

msgctxt "an11.10:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "an11.10:1.3"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an11.10:1.4"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an11.10:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.327, sc2
msgctxt "an11.10:2.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant who has three qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

msgctxt "an11.10:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an11.10:2.3"
msgid "Asekhena sīlakkhandhena, asekhena samādhikkhandhena, asekhena paññākkhandhena—"
msgstr "The entire spectrum of an adept’s ethics, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an11.10:2.4"
msgid "imehi, kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these three qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an11.10:3.1"
msgid "Aparehipi, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant who has another three qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

msgctxt "an11.10:3.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an11.10:3.3"
msgid "Iddhipāṭihāriyena, ādesanāpāṭihāriyena, anusāsanīpāṭihāriyena—"
msgstr "A demonstration of psychic power, a demonstration of revealing, and a demonstration of instruction. "

msgctxt "an11.10:3.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti, accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these three qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an11.10:4.1"
msgid "Aparehipi, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant who has another three qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

msgctxt "an11.10:4.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an11.10:4.3"
msgid "Sammādiṭṭhiyā, sammāñāṇena, sammāvimuttiyā—"
msgstr "Right view, right knowledge, and right freedom. "

msgctxt "an11.10:4.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these three qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an11.10:5.1"
msgid "Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant who has two qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

msgctxt "an11.10:5.2"
msgid "Katamehi dvīhi? "
msgstr "What two? "

msgctxt "an11.10:5.3"
msgid "Vijjāya, caraṇena—"
msgstr "Knowledge and conduct. "

msgctxt "an11.10:5.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu accantaniṭṭho hoti accantayogakkhemī accantabrahmacārī accantapariyosāno seṭṭho devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these two qualities has reached the ultimate end, the ultimate sanctuary, the ultimate spiritual life, the ultimate goal. They are best among gods and humans. "

msgctxt "an11.10:5.5"
msgid "Brahmunā pesā, bhikkhave, sanaṅkumārena gāthā bhāsitā: "
msgstr "Brahmā Sanaṅkumāra also spoke this verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an11.10:6.1"
msgid "‘Khattiyo seṭṭho janetasmiṃ, "
msgstr "‘The aristocrat is best of those people "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:6.2"
msgid "ye gottapaṭisārino; "
msgstr "who take clan as the standard. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:6.3"
msgid "Vijjācaraṇasampanno, "
msgstr "But one accomplished in knowledge and conduct "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:6.4"
msgid "so seṭṭho devamānuse’ti. "
msgstr "is best of gods and humans.’ "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.328, sc7
msgctxt "an11.10:7.1"
msgid "Sā kho panesā, bhikkhave, sanaṅkumārena gāthā bhāsitā subhāsitā, no dubbhāsitā; atthasaṃhitā, no anatthasaṃhitā; anumatā mayā. "
msgstr "Now, that verse spoken by Brahmā Sanaṅkumāra is well spoken, not poorly spoken. It’s beneficial, not pointless, and I agree with it. "

msgctxt "an11.10:7.2"
msgid "Ahampi, bhikkhave, evaṃ vadāmi: "
msgstr "I also say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an11.10:8.1"
msgid "‘Khattiyo seṭṭho janetasmiṃ, "
msgstr "‘The aristocrat is best of those people "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:8.2"
msgid "ye gottapaṭisārino; "
msgstr "who take clan as the standard. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:8.3"
msgid "Vijjācaraṇasampanno, "
msgstr "But one accomplished in knowledge and conduct "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:8.4"
msgid "so seṭṭho devamānuse’”ti. "
msgstr "Is best of gods and humans.’” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an11.10:8.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an11.10:8.6"
msgid "Nissayavaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an11.10:9.1"
msgid "Kimatthiyā cetanā tayo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:9.2"
msgid "upanisā byasanena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:9.3"
msgid "Dve saññā manasikāro, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an11.10:9.4"
msgid "saddho moranivāpakanti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
